'''多布森單位'''('''DU''')是用於衡量大氣中[[臭氧|臭氧]][[柱狀密度|柱狀密度]]的單位。大氣中臭氧主要是來自[[臭氧層|臭氧層]]。1個多布森單位是指在[[標準狀況|標準溫度與標準壓力]]下0.01毫米厚的臭氧層<ref>{{GoldBookRef|title=Dobson unit ''in atmospheric chemistry''|url=http://goldbook.iupac.org/D01827.html}}</ref>。<ref>{{cite journal|author= S. E. Schwartz|author2= P. Warneck|year= 1995|title= Units for use in atmospheric chemistry|journal= Pure Appl. Chem.|volume= 67|issue= 8-9|pages= 1377–1406|url= http://www.iupac.org/publications/pac/67/8/1377/|doi= 10.1351/pac199567081377|access-date= 2011-11-09|archive-date= 2011-06-29|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110629124211/http://www.iupac.org/publications/pac/67/8/1377/|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ozone Hole Watch|url=http://ozonewatch.gsfc.nasa.gov/|publisher=NASA|accessdate=2007-10-21|archive-date=2009-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090218212230/http://ozonewatch.gsfc.nasa.gov/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
多布森單位是紀念英國物理學家和氣象家[[戈登·多布森|戈登·多布森]](Gordon M. B. Dobson)而命名。多布森建造了第一台量度臭氧柱狀的儀器。

